window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is a SoundCraft Audiobooks production. An audio-enhanced version (with music and sound effects) of three of the greatest science fiction classics of all time - in one collection! </p> <p>H.G. Wells (1866 -1946) - the master of the genre - created his \"scientific romances\" and set the standard for prophetic and prescient scientific literature that also teemed with social commentary and even glimpses of horror. </p> <p>Enjoy these three classics by the \"Father of Science Fiction\".</p>"; 
